Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.05,0:00:05.05,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.89,0:00:07.40,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,There's a pickled plum in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.07,0:00:29.17,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.22,0:00:33.75,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.34,0:00:40.47,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're the sun, Tsumugu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.09,0:00:43.36,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's night?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.11,0:00:46.13,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,That might be why.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.84,0:00:48.36,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,You're even brighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.35,0:00:54.38,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:58.20,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I was told I couldn't go up \Nto the surface by myself yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.86,0:01:01.58,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Despite that, I always \Nlooked up to the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.40,0:01:03.95,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I admired it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.44,0:01:07.96,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond the sea, beyond the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.37,0:01:11.04,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,The sun that was so far, far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.77,0:01:13.89,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,It was so bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.89,0:01:15.74,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,It shined down on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:17.97,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,It made me warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.97,0:01:19.20,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,It made me excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:20.82,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.74,0:01:23.56,Main,Tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:09.04,Episode-Title - Left Middle,title,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Thirteen: \N Unreachable Fingertips
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.65,0:03:14.45,Italics,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's really quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.14,0:03:17.72,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Was it always this quiet at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:22.18,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought there \Nwas a lot more noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:24.61,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because it's right \Nbefore the hibernation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.36,0:03:27.81,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because the saltflake\N snow has piled up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:32.07,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.07,0:03:34.19,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one that was noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:37.77,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,When it was decided that \NNami Junior High was going
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.77,0:03:40.32,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,to be closed, and we started \Ngoing to school on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.02,0:03:42.33,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That's when it happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:45.63,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let anyone see \Nthis no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.63,0:03:47.22,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,"Anyone"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:48.90,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're already showing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:50.45,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,You're allowed, Hii-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:53.57,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka had said that... \Nbut towards Tsumugu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.62,0:03:59.34,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, there were \Nripples making noise in my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:01.10,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It got stormy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:02.20,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And when I realized it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:05.72,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,it felt like it was a ship caught in \Nthe middle of the stormy sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:08.73,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But it wasn't just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:12.98,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone cared for someone, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:15.19,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Some of us didn't realize \Nthose feelings ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:17.19,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,or know what to do with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:20.78,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And even though someone had cared \Nabout us, we couldn't realize it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:22.65,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Or couldn't respond...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:25.63,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,We were shaken, crumpled...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:29.41,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is desperately taking control \Nof the wheel and crossing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:31.05,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:34.18,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:54.02,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:56.28,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.42,0:05:01.00,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for showing up so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:03.87,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sort of glad you were outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:06.60,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Were you out on a walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:08.91,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:10.55,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:13.66,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,The moon's really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.27,0:05:16.92,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.74,0:05:19.92,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:21.32,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.79,0:05:22.92,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,About earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:24.34,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:24.34,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:28.32,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:29.91,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.26,0:05:37.81,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,About earlier, I'm sorry \NI said that so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.59,0:05:40.69,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I was sort of going with the momentum...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:44.00,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,The blood had rushed to my \Nhead and I just blurted it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:46.82,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I haven't really \Nmatured, or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:51.20,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So I wanted to say it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:52.45,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:56.27,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I... really do love you, Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:58.80,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, and you're precious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:06:00.42,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:04.83,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But Chisaki, Kaname, and Tsumugu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.83,0:06:08.24,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Akari, Miuna, and Sayu... even Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.74,0:06:10.80,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,All of you are precious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:16.00,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you like me or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:20.56,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,the fact that you're precious to \Nme won't change, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.97,0:06:30.45,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So... What were you trying \Nto say a second ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.52,0:06:32.87,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,The Ofunehiki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:34.83,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,After it's done, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:36.91,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:40.92,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun, wave the flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:44.31,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Wave it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.31,0:06:48.00,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,That way, no one will get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:06:51.04,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:29.17,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading out, Dad. Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:39.76,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,So you're going up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.88,0:07:41.81,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:43.45,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.68,0:07:45.70,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the day of the hibernation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:47.28,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:49.44,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't stay out too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:54.95,Main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do our best to stay \Nawake until you get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.52,0:07:57.83,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd try to stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:08:02.98,Main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,You were secretly eating while \Nyou were up there, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:05.08,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think we wouldn't notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:06.91,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:08.72,Main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:11.48,Main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,I hope the festival goes well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.79,0:08:13.12,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.88,0:08:17.47,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:27.97,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Chisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:29.98,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:32.50,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,So they properly sent you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:35.28,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. They said to do my \Nbest in the Ofunehiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:38.24,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness. I was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:42.92,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Kaname?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:44.32,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Did everything go okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:46.79,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time we \Never had a huge fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:49.54,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhat worked things \Nout in the end, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:51.00,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:52.57,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:56.60,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You were working really hard \Npreparing for the Ofunehiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.81,0:09:00.60,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I was just doing whatever I could
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:03.85,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,so I'd have more opportunities\Nto be together with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:05.20,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:06.56,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Chisaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:10.22,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,You might have had your hands full \Nwith your feelings for Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.22,0:09:13.26,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,But I did actually confess to you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:16.41,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course I didn't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:18.28,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I am really thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:23.94,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we do end up asleep and \Nwake up at different times,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:27.79,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,the fact that I love you won't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:29.84,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:34.66,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:38.57,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:39.84,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.84,0:09:40.85,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:42.44,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Manaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:43.71,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,She's not here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:47.03,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,And we were taking our \Ntime getting up here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:49.36,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.08,0:09:59.23,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,To be late today of all days...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.23,0:10:00.95,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,You really are amazing, Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:01.80,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:06.09,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously. She really may \Nbe the greatest of us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:07.40,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:10.33,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,You guys aren't \Ncomplimenting me... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:11.24,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Duh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.24,0:10:12.12,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:14.85,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,But Grandma was falling \Nout of her futon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:17.56,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.56,0:10:21.18,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,You're all quite lively considering \Nwe're all about to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:22.43,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Uroko-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.50,0:10:25.04,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,We came to say our greetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.04,0:10:29.06,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to go do the Ofunehiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.46,0:10:32.94,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You said it'd be pointless, \Nbut we're going to do it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:37.31,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.31,0:10:39.96,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,I will not be able to change anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:45.15,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,However, all of you may actually \Nbe able to change something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.15,0:10:46.27,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.76,0:10:52.21,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently you've grown before \NI even realized it, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:53.37,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:54.44,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:57.51,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing more to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:11:02.19,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Only... Since this started \Nbecause of what you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.44,0:11:05.46,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you don't run away, \Nno matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:08.14,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to tell me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:13.32,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Akari... to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:29.58,Ofunehiki Festival,sign,0000,0000,0000,,<Ofunehiki Festival>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:31.87,Main,Saya,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:36.42,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,A lot happened, but who \Nknew it'd get this big.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:38.25,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,0:11:39.84,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:42.37,Main,saya,0000,0000,0000,,What are you being all serious for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:44.32,Main,saya,0000,0000,0000,,You're embarrassing us! Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:45.85,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, Hikari,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:49.85,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,are you planning to be the guide of \Nthe Ofunehiki dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:51.31,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:52.94,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's just my school uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:54.02,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:55.96,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,You're a man of the sea, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:58.86,Main,saya,0000,0000,0000,,And the uniform for a \Nman of the sea is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:11:59.86,Main,both,0000,0000,0000,,That!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.73,0:12:01.86,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:05.52,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I am a person from the sea, \Nbut I'm not a man of the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:07.23,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. We're taking you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:10.61,Main,saya,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Pops. Could you turn him into \Na proper man of the sea, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:12.52,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.66,0:12:22.71,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Mo-Mom... M-Mo-Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:26.36,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,M-M-Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.42,0:12:30.22,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that'll make \NAkari-san really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:31.72,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,You... think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.72,0:12:32.57,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:35.10,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna, there's trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:36.66,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Akari transformed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:46.69,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna, it's amazing! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.69,0:12:48.15,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.50,0:12:54.72,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna, Itaru-san, thank you so much \Nfor listening to my selfish wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:55.78,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.78,0:12:59.19,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be together forever \Nnow anyway, right, Aka-cha—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:01.72,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mo—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.72,0:13:02.92,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:05.36,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,If I look at you now, \Neven though this is just for show,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:08.25,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to let\Nyou go marry the Sea God.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.25,0:13:11.56,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,So I can't look! I'll never look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:14.35,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,D-Daddy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:15.95,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Aka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.95,0:13:18.19,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Once this is over, I have \Nsomething I want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:19.22,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:20.26,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:22.57,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you later, then, Miuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:40.50,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Uroko-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:42.73,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Let us begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:18.36,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:32.39,Fishery Cooperative,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Fishery Cooperative
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.64,0:15:11.45,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Akari, accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:13.93,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,It is our gift to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:28.36,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,The sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.97,0:15:35.17,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:46.15,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:49.23,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,They're being led by sacred fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:50.53,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,Akari...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:54.26,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see, Sea God?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:16:01.77,Italics,akari,0000,0000,0000,,In this wide ocean, we may be \Nsmall, insignificant beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:06.76,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,But the people of the sea and \Nthe people of the surface
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:09.66,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,are all doing their best to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:12.28,Italics,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,We all want to be together forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:15.91,Italics,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,With the people who are \Nprecious to us, forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:20.79,Italics,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,So, Sea God, if you're really out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.78,0:16:23.79,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Sea God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:25.54,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:29.09,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hear... Our wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:52.72,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:53.80,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:57.01,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,The Sea God really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:59.78,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,...has come to take Akari-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:09.65,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Akari!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:12.17,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Akari-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.85,0:17:13.96,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Mukaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:25.64,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.77,0:17:36.86,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Akari-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:54.35,Italics,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:57.53,Italics,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's like my body won't listen to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:04.20,Italics,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.42,0:18:07.67,Italics,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.56,0:18:23.21,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,Uroko-sama! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:29.25,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:32.81,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I am the \Nscale of the Sea God.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:37.56,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:40.85,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't get up to the surface soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.85,0:18:42.55,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu-kun will...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:47.57,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.59,0:19:10.40,Main,guys,0000,0000,0000,,One, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.48,0:19:15.71,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:25.28,Main,guy b,0000,0000,0000,,Look! The bridge pier!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:45.49,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:03.04,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.04,0:20:06.99,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Akari-san has people waiting for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:09.43,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:11.68,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.68,0:20:13.19,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:16.50,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Is someone precious to someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:25.41,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't try to forcefully rip \Napart those who love each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:29.03,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist on taking someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:38.09,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,...take me instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:46.56,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:52.91,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.42,0:20:55.70,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:20:57.90,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.52,0:21:40.29,Main,people,0000,0000,0000,,Look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.29,0:21:41.94,Main,people,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's floating!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:43.07,Main,people,0000,0000,0000,,Get the boat out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.14,0:21:46.21,Main,people,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.51,0:21:48.00,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:50.19,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,Akari!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.10,0:23:33.97,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I look from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.51,0:23:39.17,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,To the sea where Hikari \Nand the others are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:40.06,Episode-Title,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Fourteen: \NThe Promised Day
